
= numeric_i

  Take complex values easy.

== Description

  This tiny code snippet adds a method named "i" to Numeric in order to get
  complex values more easily.

== Installation

=== Archive Installation

	rake install

=== Gem Installation

	gem install numeric_i


== Features/Problems

  + Providing a method Numeric#i which takes an imaginary number of the numeric.

== Synopsis
  
  require 'rubygems'
  require 'numeric_i'

  1 + 1.i #=> Complex(1, 1)


